OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FScattered heavy showers mixed
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells will ease by early
OL,7,Fafternoon as cloud starts to thicken.
OL,8,FOutbreaks of rain are possible by dusk
OL,9,Fover western hills. Strong and gusty
OL,10,Fwinds easing later. Mild, but feeling
OL,11,Fcooler in the wind.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy, with rain spreading
OL,14,Feastwards during the evening, perhaps
OL,15,Fwith some heavier bursts. Mostly dry
OL,16,Fby dawn, with a few clear spells.
OL,17,FBecoming breezy again later in the
OL,18,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
