OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FOften cloudy and mostly dry,
OL,6,Falthough some drizzly outbreaks are
OL,7,Fpossible, mostly on western hills.
OL,8,FSome brighter spells, mainly for
OL,9,Feastern parts. Breezy, with strong
OL,10,Fgusts over high ground.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FOften
OL,13,Fcloudy Wednesday and Thursday, with
OL,14,Foccasional rain. Perhaps drier,
OL,15,Fbrighter in the east. Breezy and mild.
OL,16,FFriday likely wet and windy at first,
OL,17,Fthen cooler with showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
